songs.title: Beep Beep
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: All]
Beep beep, ah, ooh, ah, beep beep, ah, ooh, ah

[Verse 1: Jade Thirlwall, All & Leigh-Anne Pinnock]
I'm stuck in traffic, bumper to bumper, babe
My leather jacket smells like your aftershave
All I wanna do is get your hands up on my booty
(Beep beep, ah, ooh, ah)
I blew my engine, I think I broke the stick
Too busy dreaming, of jumping on your—
To get me turning good, you need to check under the hood, babe
(Beep beep, ah, ooh, ah)

[Pre-Chorus: Perrie Edwards & All]
Oh, baby, baby
There's something about your love and affection (Ah, ah, ah, ahh-ah)
I'm going crazy
The thought of you is driving me wild (Ooh, ooh, ooh-ooh)

[Chorus: All, Jade Thirlwall & Leigh-Anne Pinnock]
'Cause I love, love, love, making love to you
But I'm stuck, stuck, stuck, on the 202
Won't you help me, help me?
Just wanna— you tonight
(Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh) Beep beep, ahh, ooh, ahh
Baby, pump, pump, pump, 'cause I'm in a jam
Give me a jump, jump, jump, make it start again
Won't you help me, help me?
Just wanna— you tonight
(Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh) Beep beep, ahh, ooh, ahh

[Verse 2: Jesy Nelson & All]
Boy, you're so sexy, just like your Cadillac
Just come and get me, 'cause I can't hold it back
People on the street watch us in the backseat, oh
(Beep beep, ahh, ooh, ahh)

[Pre-Chorus: Jade Thirlwall & All]
Oh, baby, baby
There's something about your love and affection (Ah, ah, ah, ahh-ah)
I'm going crazy
The thought of you is driving me wild (Ooh, ooh, ooh-ooh) (Ooh)

[Chorus: All, Perrie Edwards & Jesy Nelson]
'Cause I love, love, love, making love to you
But I'm stuck, stuck, stuck, on the 202
Won't you help me, help me?
Just wanna— you tonight
(Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh) Beep beep, ahh, ooh, ahh
Baby, pump, pump, pump, 'cause I'm in a jam
Give me a jump, jump, jump, make it start again
Won't you help me, help me?
Just wanna— you tonight
(Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh) Beep beep, ahh, ooh, ahh

[Bridge: Jade Thirlwall with Leigh-Anne Pinnock & Jesy Nelson]
I'll push that pedal 'til it's gone through the floor
I'm running reds like I would run from the law
I'll push that pedal 'til it's gone through the floor (Gone through the floor)
I'm running reds like I would run from the law (Yeah)

[Breakdown: Leigh-Anne Pinnock & Perrie Edwards]
Mmmh, ahh, yeah (Hey!)

[Chorus: All, Jade Thirlwall, Perrie Edwards, Leigh-Anne Pinnock & (Jesy Nelson)]
'Cause I love, love, love, making love to (Lo-o-ove) you (Baby)
But I'm stuck, stuck, stuck, on the 202
Won't you help me, help me?
Just wanna— you tonight
(Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh) Beep beep (Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh), ahh, ooh, ahh
(Yeah) Baby, pump, pump, pump, 'cause I'm in a (Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh) jam
Give me a jump, jump, jump, make it start again (Oh, baby)
Won't you help me, help me?
Just wanna— you tonight
(Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh) Beep beep, ahh, ooh, ahh (Ohh, ohh, ohh, yeah, yeah)

[Outro: Perrie Edwards & All]
Now looky here! (Love, love, love)
I need ya, baby! I wantcha, (Stuck, stuck, stuck) baby
Gotta have ya baby, woo! (Help me, help me)
Help me out! I need some lovin' (Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh)
Yee-hee, ah!
